1. What is the MVC pattern?
Model View Controller
Model View Components

A model represents data 
The view is how the data is rendered, the portion the user sees, views.,the user interface.
The Controller (angular1 being phased out(clicks/user events)) in favor of Components.

A component is a small/reusable package of both front and back end code that work together.


